  "text": "Finally, there is a large amount of related work through the participants of Semeval 2013 Task 2, and Semeval 2014 Task9: Sentiment Analysis in Twitter [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . A full list of teams and results can be found in the task description papers.",
